e for the biggest banks.=C2=A0
A general feature of the Fed=E2=80=99s stress tests is that, when the Fed s=
erves up a =E2=80=9Cseverely adverse=E2=80=9D stress scenario to the banks,=
 the banks go off and model the effect it would have on their business, and=
