he big banks, and it=E2=80=99s perfectly plausible that some scenarios woul=
d be=C2=A0bad=C2=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0for the world, for the economy, for the b=
anking system =E2=80=94=C2=A0while also being=C2=A0good for the big banks. =
