Technology Group, a company backed by Donald Trump that would soon be launc=
hing a social network called TRUTH Social.   I was skeptical at the time, b=
ecause I figured (1) Donald Trump would probably not be launching a social =
network? but (2) doing this sort of SPAC deal was a good way for him to rai=
se some money from enthusiastic retail investors. I have to say, I seem to =
