<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yes.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Now, this year=E2=80=99s stress test <em>did <=
/em>include another scenario for the eight biggest banks, which (1) is=C2=
=A0<em>different=C2=A0</em>from the regular stress test and (2) is closer t=
