e" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">My view</a> is that this is kind of =
silly in this case:=C2=A0Investors weren=E2=80=99t=C2=A0<em>harmed </em>by =
the lies, since after all they were thrilled when the Trump deal was announ=
